{
  "texts": [
    "As we increase model capacity from 1.5B to 7B, the win-rate against expert human poems grows substantially, from 7.8% to 25.0%.",
    "The scoring evaluation similarly improves from 67.8 to 77.3.",
    "This trend shows that just like verifiable domains, RARO continues to effective scale with model size in open-ended domains.",
    "Emergent Qualitative Reasoning.",
    "Qualitatively, RARO induces explicit planning and reasoning behaviors even in open-ended domains."
  ]
}